# 🚀 Deal Digger Compass

A modern web application designed to help users discover, analyze, and track the best deals efficiently. Built with a scalable frontend architecture and optimized for performance, usability, and real-time interaction.

---

## 📌 Overview

Deal Digger Compass is a smart deal discovery platform that aggregates and presents valuable offers in a structured and user-friendly interface. The project focuses on delivering a seamless experience with fast rendering, responsive design, and modular components.

This project demonstrates strong fundamentals in frontend engineering, component-based architecture, and modern web tooling.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🔍 Deal Discovery Interface – Browse and explore curated deals  
- ⚡ Fast Performance – Powered by Vite  
- 🎨 Modern UI/UX – Built with Tailwind CSS and shadcn/ui  
- 📱 Responsive Design – Works across all devices  
- 🧩 Component-Based Architecture – Clean and reusable code  
- 🔄 Extendable – Ready for API and real-time data integration  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Frontend: React (TypeScript)  
- Build Tool: Vite  
- Styling: Tailwind CSS  
- UI Components: shadcn/ui  
- Linting: ESLint  

---

